#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<'EOF'
Releases are automated with release-please.

1. Push conventional commits to main (feat:, fix:, refactor:, docs: ...).
2. release-please maintains a "Release PR" that bumps the version
   (manifest.json + pyproject.toml) and updates CHANGELOG.md.
3. Merge the Release PR when ready — the tag, GitHub release and the
   smartir.zip asset are published automatically.

No manual tagging required.
EOF
